title: No Regrets (Delta Force #1) by Shannon K. Butcher. EPUB (Perseu)
description:
Renowned cryptologist Noelle Blanche refuses to have
blood on her hands. So when the military asks for her
help in a covert operation, she refuses--until masked
gunmen raid her home and threaten her life. Suddenly
it's all too clear that any blood spilled may be her
own. Noelle has no choice but to trust the dangerous
stranger sent by the military to safeguard her.
A stranger who is everything she detests, everything
she fears...and everything she desires.
